Do you want to be the hero and save these patients? Now you have the chance in this management game Fight Virus! You need to click on those viruses to kill them, if you miss one of them, there will be more and more viruses. See how long you can survive in the game Fight Virus!
Mouse click or tap the screen to play

item.content:encoded:
Foodtycoon Frvr is a good managing game. Owning a coffee shop is every girl’s dream, now it comes true! You are mastering a little coffee shop, learn how to manage it, and how the shop keeps running well. I will teach you how to make drinks, with your level up you could make more kinds of drinks. Customers will get more and more, their Purchase demand is also more strange, but you have to satisfy them. You will get busier, improve your equipment to cook faster, you can also upgrade the materials that earn more money! Collect keys to unlock more characters!
Click to cook

item.content:encoded:
Doggo Clicker is a fun clicker game that lets you click your cute dog. His mood becomes better when you click him. There are 50 different upgrades and 21 accessories, make him look more cool and nice. Level up, spend your stat points, and progress faster. Also, there are 2 layers of prestige and a house to built, have fun.
Left mouse button.
